'''''Defcon 5''''' is a 1987 video game by [[Cosmi Corporation|Cosmi]], created by [[Paul Norman (game designer)|Paul Norman]]. It was released first for the [[Commodore 64]], and then ported to the [[Amiga]] and [[DOS]].

==Gameplay==
''Defcon 5'' is a game which is set during the Cold War era.<ref name=cgw150/>

